Package cs2030s.fp

Class InfiniteList<T>

java.lang.Object
cs2030s.fp.InfiniteList<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
InfiniteList.Sentinel
public class InfiniteList<T> extends Object
Represents an infinite list of elements of type T that is lazily evaluated.
